Project Name: Sayf AI Text Fixer
Description:  AI-powered bilingual text correction tool using Google Gemini API
Language:     AutoHotkey v2.0+
Platform:     Microsoft Windows 10/11

THIRD-PARTY DEPENDENCIES:
- AutoHotkey v2.0+ (GPLv2 License) - https://www.autohotkey.com/
- Google Gemini API (Google Terms of Service) - https://ai.google.dev/
- JSON Library by G33kDude (MIT License) - https://github.com/G33kDude/cJson.ahk

API USAGE DISCLAIMER:
This software integrates with Google Gemini API. Users are responsible for:
- Obtaining their own API keys from Google AI Studio
- Complying with Google's Terms of Service and Usage Policies
- Any costs associated with API usage
- Data privacy and security when using cloud AI services

PRIVACY NOTICE:
- Text processed through this software is sent to Google's Gemini API
- No text content is stored locally beyond session logs (user configurable)
- Users should review Google's privacy policy for cloud AI services
- Sensitive or confidential text should not be processed without proper authorization

